Heya' brother!

You've been a great companion. As far as I remember, we first met in our Department's Freshers' Welcome Party. You were a shy, innocent and sweet guy then; amazed us with your juggling!

These 4 years, you've changed a lot. Not the shy and innocent guy, although still very sweet. And totally helpful! Thanks for being there when I needed you brother! We still have at least an year together, and we still have a lot of moments to enjoy. 

Hope we'll meet soon!
